      <div class="span6"> 
       <h2 class="tit">NBC's New Olympics Deal Means A Windfall For The NBA</h2> 
       <div class="titArea undis">
        <form action="/edit/title/471f23f193e6210910328ee811d10fce/" id="postTitle" method="post">
         <textarea name="title">nbc的新奥运合同意味着对nba的横财</textarea>
         <a href="javascript:;" class="btn4 mt10 mr10" id="postTitle"><span class="loading" style="display:none">保存中</span><span id="saveTitle">保存</span></a>
         <a href="javascript:;" class="titCancel">取消</a>
        </form>
       </div> 
       <div class="titSub">
        <h1 id="titleCn">nbc的新奥运合同意味着对nba的横财</h1>
        <a href="javascript:;" class="btn1 editBtn">修改标题</a>
       </div> 
       <p class="author">作者：<a href="/search/Peter%20Lauria/" target="_blank"> Peter Lauria</a></p> 
       <p class="titBar"> <span class="time">时间：2014-05-08</span> <span class="read">阅读：269</span> <span class="source">来源：<a href="http://www.buzzfeed.com/peterlauria/nbcs-new-olympics-deal-means-a-windfall-for-the-nba" target="_blank" rel="“nofollow”">buzzfeed</a></span> </p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="span2"> 
       <div class="recom"> 
        <div class="recomBox " data-article_id="471f23f193e6210910328ee811d10fce"> 
         <p class="num">0</p> 
         <p class="txt">推荐</p> 
        </div> 
        <div class="addNum">
         +1
        </div> 
       </div> 
